### Cross-Border Business Payments

Pay vendors and partners globally using Stellar infrastructure.

### Invoice Generation

Generate professional invoices with embedded payment options.
Customers can pay directly through supported payment rails.

### Treasury Dashboard

Track:
Cash flow
Balances
Currency exposure
