in real time.

## Why Fluxa Matters

Millions of African businesses are increasingly global.
However, financial infrastructure has not kept pace.
Fluxa leverages Stellar to provide businesses with access to:
Global payments
Digital dollars
Treasury tools
Modern financial services
without requiring them to understand blockchain technology.
For the user, the experience feels like modern business banking.
For the infrastructure, Stellar provides the settlement layer.

## Revenue Model

Fluxa generates revenue through:

### FX Conversion

Fees on USDC-to-local-currency conversions.

### Cross-Border Payments

Transaction fees on business payments.

### Treasury Services

Premium treasury and reporting tools.

### Subscription Plans

Advanced business accounts and team features.

### API Access

Infrastructure services for fintechs and marketplaces.

