## Vision

We believe every African business should have access to the global economy.
Fluxa is building the financial operating system for African commerce using Stellar as the settlement layer.
Our long-term vision is a future where any entrepreneur in Africa can receive, manage, convert, and move money globally without friction, regardless of location or banking limitations.

